INFORMATION WE COLLECT (SCOPE AND CATEGORIES OF PERSONAL DATA)

“Information” could be either personal information or non-personal information, information you make available or combination that relates to you, and can be used to identify you. In providing our Services, we collect, store and use the following information relating to you:

There are a few basic categories of information we collect:

Information which you make available when you use our Services, including shared information you make available to others through our Services and information you store our Services.
Information you choose to give us when you open an account or use our Services, such as your email address, your telephone number, your introduction, and your birthday;
Shared information we receive from others using our Services, such as information contained in posts they make and other using our Services; and information we collect as you use our Services, such as certain location data and log data.
Information You Choose to Give Us & Make Available to Us

Information and Content You Provide. Besides the basic information we request when you sign up (including register e-mail, nickname, password, avatar, country, gender, birthday, name, profile, display name, login device, device No, signature, language, website, Youtube account), we also collect the content and other information you provide when you use our Services, including when you sign up for an account, create or share content.
Non-personal Information. Including any information related to you but from which it is not practicable to directly identify you.

Location Data. We collect information regarding your location (when you use a location-enable service), including the location of you device when you use our Services, such as from the GPS, WIFI, compass, accelerometer or other sensors in you mobile device; the IP address of the device or internet service you use to access our Services; other information made available by you or others that indicated where you are located and shared information you or others post indicating your location, such as any geotag information that is embedded in any photos you make available to us; and if you have provided us with your location data previously and would like us to delete such existing location data, you may be able to do so via our Services.

Device Information and Log Data. We collect technical information automatically when you use our Services, whether through the use of cookies, web beacons and log files or otherwise, including technical information such as your mobile carrier, configuration information made available by your web browser or other programs you use to access our Services, your IP address and your device’s version and identification number.

Browsing and Searching History. Information about what you have searched for and looked at while using our Services, such as web search terms used, social media profiles visited and details of other information and content accessed or requested by you in using our Services.

The Data Subject agrees that while providing the Services the Operator has the right to use statistical data and other tracking technologies (Cookies) for their following processing provided that this data is anonymized and cannot be attributed to you as an identified and identifiable individual.

Shared Information We Collect from Others

Things other users do and information they provide about you. You agree that we may receive and analyze content and information that other people provide when they use our Services. This can include information about you, such as when others share or comment on a photo of you, send a message to you.

From other services. If you link your Oh My Vap account to another service, we may receive information from the other service, like how you use that service. Advertisers may let us know you installed a new app or game so we can determine whether we showed you an ad for it. If you interact with one of our advertisers, they may share information with us to help target or measure the performance of ads. If you link your Oh My Vap account to another service as described, this means that you agree with such processing of data.

HOW WE USE PERSONAL INFORMATION, PURPOSES OF PROCESSING

How we use. The personal data processing is performed by the following means: collecting, recording, systemizing, accumulating, storing, specifying (updating, changing), extracting, using, transferring, depersonalizing, blocking, deleting and destroying.

The personal data is processed by means of automatization (automated processing).

We processes the personal data individually or entrust processing to third parties. If We entrust processing to the third parties We will include information on them to the Policy, inter alia, by means of including the list using the corresponding link which forms an integral part of this Policy.

Purposes of processing. Personal data processing is limited by achieving a clear, predefined and lawful purpose. Personal data processing is prohibited if such processing is incompatible with the purpose of processing specified in this Policy.

The purpose of our processing of your data is to provide you with an amazing set of Services that we relentlessly improve. Here are the ways we do that:

develop, operate, improve, deliver, maintain, and protect our Services;
for customer service, security, fraud-detection, archival and backup purposes in connection with the provision of our services;
provide you with advertising and direct marketing that is more relevant to you (as discussed in more detail below under the “direct marketing” section below);
to better understanding how you access and use our Services, for the purposed of trying to improve our Services and to respond to user desires and preferences, including language and location customization, personalized help and instructions, or other responses to your and other users’ usage of our services;
to access the effectiveness of and improve advertising and other marketing and promotional activities on or in connection with our services when your account is subscribed to an official account; and
to allow you to participate in surveys about Services. If you participate in a survey, we may request certain personally identifiable information from you, participation in these surveys is voluntary and you therefore have a choice whether or not to disclose this information, the surveys. We use third party service provider will be prohibited from using your personally identifiable information for any other purpose.
Please note that the purposes of seeking to provide our Users with a better experience, to improve our Services or otherwise where you have consented, personal information collected through our site or Service may, subject to user privacy controls (where available), be used by our other Services (including in an aggregated or individualized manner).

We processes only such personal data which matches predefined purpose of processing. We do not collect and process personal data, which is not necessary to achievement of the purpose, set out in this Privacy Policy and the Operator does not use the personal data for purposes other than declared in the Privacy Policy.

