Performance of the Terms of Service and provisions of the Services to Users,
Consents of Users.
The Operator may process personal data on other legal grounds, allowed by the Russian law, for example:
for statistical or other research purposes provided that the personal data is anonymized in a mandatory manner;
if the Data Subject or at his/her request grants access to his/her personal data for the general public;
if the personal data must be published or compulsorily disclosed under the legislation of the Russian Federation.
