HOW LONG WE KEEP YOUR INFORMATION
We store data until it is no longer necessary to provide our Services, or until your account is deleted - whichever occurs first. This could be a case-by-case determination that depends on things like the nature of the data, why it is collected and processed, and relevant legal or operational retention needs.

When you delete your account, we also delete content you have posted, such as your photos and status updates, and you may not be able to recover that information later. Information that others have shared about you isn't part of your account and won't be deleted.

Subject to applicable and regulations (including as set out under the “How We Use / Share Your Personal Information” sections above), we will only use your personal information for so long as is necessary to fulfill the purposes as set out under the section above.

Subject to applicable laws and regulations, you may have the right to request to receive a copy of and make any corrections to your personal information which we hold, and to request that we deactivate and not use any of your personal information that is stored by us, you may direct such request to our privacy officer at service@Oh My Vap.com, or where we offer this option in our Services ,you may also log into your account with us and make the appropriate changed. We will respond to all requests made to our privacy officer under this “retention of your personal information” section within 60 days.

We also erase your information in the following situations (if applicable and depending on the situation):

recall of the consent by the Data Subject (when such content was required for processing);
revealing unjustified personal data processing;
achieving the predefined purpose of personal data processing;
the Operator’s liquidation.
Please note that if you recall your consent (a) Oh My Vap may stop rendering you Oh My Vap Services if this is technically impossible without the data you recalled your consent for, and (b) Oh My Vap may keep processing some of your data, determined on a case by case basis, if Oh My Vap has other legal ground to process it, such as e.g. a requirement of a federal law.

